    • flags

      public int flags()
      Description copied from interface: CharacterRange
      A flags word, indicating the kind of range. Multiple flag bits may be set. Valid flags include Classfile.CRT_STATEMENT, Classfile.CRT_BLOCK, Classfile.CRT_ASSIGNMENT, Classfile.CRT_FLOW_CONTROLLER, Classfile.CRT_FLOW_TARGET, Classfile.CRT_INVOKE, Classfile.CRT_CREATE, Classfile.CRT_BRANCH_TRUE, Classfile.CRT_BRANCH_FALSE.
